cff-version: 1.2.0
message: If you use this software in your research, please cite it as below.
type: software
title: hapax-swarm
abstract: |
  Filesystem-as-bus multi-session coordination library extracted from
  the Hapax operating environment. Implements the relay protocol,
  claim-before-parallel-work primitive, and cc-task SSOT pattern that
  drove a 30+ PR/day single-operator velocity result over the
  hapax-council monorepo. Reusable shape: any caller pointing at a
  shared relay directory inherits the same coordination guarantees
  across N peer Claude Code sessions.
